headline: Netflix Stock Has A January Superpower — And The Numbers Prove It
summary: Netflix Inc. (NASDAQ:NFLX) has developed a striking seasonal pattern that traders have come to recognize: January has historically been its strongest month of the year, and by a wide margin.
